92x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/megan_thee_stallion-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·泰恩（Megan Thee）</a>在与YouTuber和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tory-Lanez">Tory Lanez的</a>支持者Milagro Gramz的第一轮比赛中取得了成功。</p><p> 10月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-sues-youtuber-over-alleged-tory-lanez-lies-and-deepfake-porn-causing-intentional-infliction-of-emotional-distress-3808487">说唱歌手对格拉姆兹（Milagro Elizabeth Cooper）提起诉讼</a>，指控她与莱恩斯（Lanez）分享了梅根（Megan）的深层色情片和蔓延性。该诉讼还指责格拉姆兹“网络群，有意造成情绪困扰以及侵犯隐私”。</p><p>现在，佛罗里达州的一名法官裁定，梅根在提出了一个“令人信服的案件”后，可以继续对格拉姆兹提起诉讼，即博客作者在关于说唱歌手的帖子中以“鲁ck对真相的无视事实”行事。</p><p>首席法官塞西莉亚·奥尔顿加（Cecilia Altonaga）在<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/megan-thee-stallion-tory-lanez-blogger-lawsuit-moves-forward-1235259083/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>滚石公司</i></a>获得的法院文件中还说，格拉姆斯的职位“描绘了一项运动，而不是新闻业”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3822018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3822018" style="width: 2160px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3822018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg" alt="梅根你种马。图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Wireimage" width="2160" height="2700" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage.jpg 2160w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/megan-thee-stallion-2160x2700-Jamie-McCarthy_WireImage-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2160px) 100vw, 2160px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3822018" class="wp-caption-text">梅根你种马。图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Wireimage</figcaption></figure><p>法官写道：“被告轻描淡写了这些指控（诽谤和出于&#39;纯粹的仇恨&#39;）的指控，认为&#39;恶意&#39;和未能调查并没有确定实际恶意。” “但是原告的主张远远超出了仅仅疏忽的范围 - 他们描绘了一场故意破坏她声誉的竞选活动的照片。这足以满足诉状标准。”</p><p>为了回应裁决，格拉姆斯的律师迈克尔·潘西尔（Michael Pancier）说：“这一决定并不能反映出对案件的优点的决心。原告现在必须通过可靠和可接受的证据来证实她的主张。”</p><p>去年12月，梅根（Megan）的律师在说他们通过传票获得了兰尼斯（Lanez）的监狱电话后，更新了诉讼，他们声称这表明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-accused-of-working-with-youtuber-to-harass-megan-thee-stallion-from-prison-3821909">说唱歌手仍在与格拉姆兹（Gramz）从后面的梅根（Gramz）对付梅根（Megan）进行骚扰</a>。</p><p>去年八月，兰尼斯因在2020年7月发生的事件而被判处10年徒刑，当时梅根在凯莉·詹纳（Kylie Jenner）的家中被枪杀时被枪杀。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-found-guilty-of-shooting-megan-thee-stallion-3371194">被判犯有针对他的所有三项指控罪</a>：一项半自动枪支的袭击罪；一项在车辆中携带隐藏，装载和未注册的枪支的罪名； <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-hit-with-third-charge-in-megan-thee-stallion-trial-3361799">并指控以严重的疏忽释放枪支</a>。这位说唱歌手塞格（Singer）从狱中维持了自己的纯真，并<a href="https://www.hotnewhiphop.com/824266-tory-lanez-small-legal-victory-hip-hop-news">获得了今年7月判决的机会</a>。</p><p>从那以后，梅根<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-wins-restraining-order-against-tory-lanez-after-tearful-testimony-hell-shoot-me-again-and-maybe-this-time-i-wont-make-it-3827774">（Megan）告诉法院担心，如果兰尼斯（Lanez）被释放，她可能会再次被枪杀，从而成功获得了针对兰尼斯（Lanez）的五年限制令</a>。</p><p>梅根（Megan）在她的纪录片<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-announces-new-documentary-in-her-words-3802734"><i>梅根·泰（Megan Thee）种马中公开了这一事件：用她的话</i></a>，通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">亚马逊Prime视频</a>发行。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-pens-final-response-on-tory-lanez-trial-people-treated-my-trauma-like-a-running-joke-3433352">她还对事件发出了“最终”回应</a>，在提出索赔时，她对她在公众面临的“屈辱”中进行了反思。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-wins-legal-round-against-youtuber-and-tory-lanez-supporter-3836201">梅根·泰（Megan Thee）的邮政投掷后，与YouTuber和Tory Lanez的支持者赢得了法律巡回赛，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
